### 状态流转测试案例
### 说明：以下请求按顺序执行，{{caseId}} 使用创建案件返回的 id。

### 1. DRAFT -> SUBMITTED：当事人提交立案
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{partyToken}}

{
  "action": "SUBMIT",
  "comment": "提交立案"
}

### 2. SUBMITTED -> FILING_REVIEW：书记员进入审核
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clerkToken}}

{
  "action": "START_REVIEW",
  "comment": "材料进入审核"
}

### 3. FILING_REVIEW -> ACCEPTED：法官审核受理
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{judgeToken}}

{
  "action": "ACCEPT",
  "comment": "符合立案条件"
}

### 4. ACCEPTED -> PAYMENT_PENDING：书记员生成缴费通知
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clerkToken}}

{
  "action": "PAYMENT_NOTICE",
  "comment": "生成诉讼费缴费通知"
}

### 5. PAYMENT_PENDING -> PAID：当事人确认缴费
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{partyToken}}

{
  "action": "CONFIRM_PAYMENT",
  "comment": "已完成缴费"
}

### 6. PAID -> EVIDENCE_SUBMITTING：开启举证
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clerkToken}}

{
  "action": "OPEN_EVIDENCE",
  "comment": "开启举证期限"
}

### 7. EVIDENCE_SUBMITTING -> SCHEDULED：排期开庭
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clerkToken}}

{
  "action": "SCHEDULE_TRIAL",
  "comment": "完成开庭排期"
}

### 8. SCHEDULED -> IN_TRIAL：开始庭审
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{judgeToken}}

{
  "action": "START_TRIAL",
  "comment": "开始庭审"
}

### 9. IN_TRIAL -> JUDGEMENT_PENDING：转入待判决
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{judgeToken}}

{
  "action": "JUDGEMENT_PENDING",
  "comment": "庭审结束，等待裁判"
}

### 10. JUDGEMENT_PENDING -> JUDGED：发布判决
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{judgeToken}}

{
  "action": "PUBLISH_JUDGEMENT",
  "comment": "发布判决书"
}

### 11. JUDGED -> APPEAL_PERIOD：进入上诉期
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clerkToken}}

{
  "action": "ENTER_APPEAL_PERIOD",
  "comment": "判决送达，进入上诉期"
}

### 12. APPEAL_PERIOD -> EFFECTIVE：确认生效
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clerkToken}}

{
  "action": "CONFIRM_EFFECTIVE",
  "comment": "上诉期届满未上诉，判决生效"
}

### 13. EFFECTIVE -> EXECUTION_PENDING：申请执行
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{partyToken}}

{
  "action": "APPLY_EXECUTION",
  "comment": "申请强制执行"
}

### 14. EXECUTION_PENDING -> EXECUTING：开始执行
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{judgeToken}}

{
  "action": "START_EXECUTION",
  "comment": "执行立案"
}

### 15. EXECUTING -> CLOSED：结案
POST http://localhost:9004/api/cases/{{caseId}}/transitions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{judgeToken}}

{
  "action": "CLOSE",
  "comment": "执行完毕，案件结案"
}
